      "span_text": "All samples were imaged with a Zeiss LSM 510 laser-scanning confocal microscope (Confocal Microscopy Laboratory, The City College of New York) using a Plan-Apochromat ϫ63/1.4 Oil DIC objective, and the image stacks were analyzed with ImageJ software (version 1.46; NIH), as previously described"
